Summary: Saw Two Objects on the Same Day This One Looks Like a Missle
trends: There have been 105 other sightings in Tampa
There was one other sighting in Tampa on or around February 25th 2010
divs: Sighting DetailsI was just looking out my window in broad daylight when I looked up all of a sudden I saw a blackish gray missle object that didn't have any wings except back fins you would see on a fish. The object was very low just above the tree line, and big. Could have been something to do with Obama's visit here, or a UFO.
